{
  "texts": [
    "Based on the findings of Gartner, it is observed that the top 10 suppliers of RPA software together own a market share above 70% within the RPA industry [23].",
    "The organizations that have been identified as leaders in the 2020 Gartner Magic Quadrant for RPA are Blue Prism, Automation Anywhere, and UiPath.",
    "UiPathUiPath, a company established in Romania in 2005, now has a dominant position in the industry for RPA.",
    "The organization has branches in a total of 19 nations and sustains a workforce of over 3100 individuals.",
    "UiPath, on December 17, 2020 [24], confidentially filed a draft registration statement with the United States Securities and Exchange Commission, expressing its intention to proceed with an initial public offering."
  ]
}